@beep/html — third-party data attribution
==========================================

The HTML element/attribute schemas in this package are generated from data
derived from the following sources. Attribution is required and provided here.

1. W3C webref (https://github.com/w3c/webref) and reffy (https://github.com/w3c/reffy)
   - Files: data/webref/dfns-html.json, data/webref/elements-html.json
   - License: MIT. Copyright (c) W3C.

2. WHATWG HTML Living Standard (https://html.spec.whatwg.org/)
   - Derived data: data/whatwg/content-model.json (parsed from indices.html)
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0).
   - "HTML Standard" by WHATWG, used under CC-BY-4.0.

These upstream sources are themselves extracted from the WHATWG HTML Standard.
Generated schema source under src/ is a derivative of the above and carries the
same attribution obligations.
